- **[Snopes](https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/trump-visit-maui-wildfires/)** also notes that the claim about Trump visiting Maui after the August 2023 fires is **false**.

Therefore, the information suggesting that Donald Trump visited Maui after the August 2023 wildfires is **not accurate** and **lacks evidence**.
